<! [CDATA[
Inspur Logo
Inspur, whose full name is Inspur Group, is an information technology enterprise in mainland China focusing on cloud computing, big data, key application hosts, servers, storage, artificial intelligence and ERP. On April 18, 2006, Inspur changed its English name from Langchao to Inspur. It is listed on the SSE, SZSE, and SEHK. It owns Inspur Information, Inspur Software, Inspur International and Huaguang Optoelectronics, and VIT, C.A.. It provides IT products and services to more than 100 countries.
You can download theInspurlogo on full-version of the page.
